---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Andre & Barbara: Nossa História Completa">
    <main class="love-story-container">
        <section class="hero-section">
            <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
            <div class="hero-content">
                <h1 class="lovers-name">A Nossa História</h1>
                <p class="love-subtitle">A jornada de dois corações, completamente apaixonados</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="our-journey">
            <div class="journey-content">
                <div class="journey-chapter">
                    <h2>O Início</h2>
                    <div class="chapter-details">
                        <div class="chapter-images">
                            <img src="/Andre1.0.jpg" alt="Andre" class="chapter-image"/>
                            <img src="/6E84FC44-31F8-4BBF-81AB-493E704FB250.JPG" alt="Barbara" class="chapter-image"/>
                        </div>
                        <p>
                            O nosso amor nasceu de um encontro improvável. Dois corações de diferentes origens  
                            unidos por uma conexão inexplicável e profunda. 
                            Desde o primeiro encontro, sentimos que havia algo especial que nos conectava, 
                            algo que transcendia palavras e explicações.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="journey-timeline">
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <h3>Primeiro Encontro</h3>
                            <p>Um momento mágico que mudou nossas vidas para sempre. Combinámos ir a um café e falámos durante horas, sobre tudo e mais alguma coisa, acabando este lindo e maravilhoso dia beijando-nos, com a chuva a começar a cair.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <h3>Descobrindo O Nosso Amor</h3>
                            <p>A primeira vez que fui a casa dela. Ela estava com o período e por isso estava cheia de dores, então combinámos ficar em casa dela, onde eu conheci a familia dela, e passei a tarde toda a cuidar dela e a fazer-lhe carinho.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <h3>O Pedido de Namoro</h3>
                            <p>Após três semanas a conhecermo-nos eu achei que devia pedir-lhe em namoro. Depois dela ter passado o Halloween em minha casa, eu decidi dar-lhe a primeira rosa, no dia 2 de Novembro de 2023 e, no dia seguinte, pedir-lhe em namoro, pois apercebi-me o quão apaixonado por ela estava.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="love-moments">
                    <div class="moments-grid">
                        <div class="moment-card">
                            <img src="/fab952ef-1e63-4db9-90df-17eb89a72536.JPG" alt="Momento Especial 1"/>
                            <div class="moment-overlay">
                                <h3>Nois</h3>
                                <p>Nos juntos</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="moment-card">
                            <img src="/IMG_2690.jpg" alt="Momento Especial 2"/>
                            <div class="moment-overlay">
                                <h3>Uma das Primeiras Fotos</h3>
                                <p>Te amo</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="moment-card">
                            <img src="/IMG_3645.jpg" alt="Momento Especial 3"/>
                            <div class="moment-overlay">
                                <h3>Nosso Amor</h3>
                                <p>Dia dos Namorados</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="love-philosophy">
            <div class="philosophy-content">
                <blockquote>
                    O nosso amor transcende línguas, culturas e fronteiras. 
                    Somos a prova de que o amor verdadeiro não conhece limites.
                </blockquote>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>

<style>
    :root {
        --deep-red: #8B0000;
        --rich-crimson: #DC143C;
        --elegant-burgundy: #800020;
        --love-pink: #FFB6C1;
        --romantic-pink: #FFC0CB;
    }

    .love-story-container {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem;
    }

    .hero-section {
        position: relative;
        height: 60vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        text-align: center;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--love-pink), var(--romantic-pink));
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
        border-radius: 15px;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-overlay {
        display: none;
    }

    .hero-content {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        animation: floatIn 1.5s ease-out;
    }

    .lovers-name {
        font-size: 4rem;
        color: white;
        text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        opacity: 0;
        animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out forwards;
    }

    .love-subtitle {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
        color: white;
        opacity: 0;
        animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out forwards 0.3s;
    }

    .journey-content {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 4rem 2rem;
        background: white;
        border-radius: 15px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .journey-chapter {
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
        opacity: 0;
        animation: slideUp 1s ease-out forwards;
    }

    .journey-chapter h2 {
        font-size: 3rem;
        color: var(--elegant-burgundy);
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .chapter-details {
        display: flex;
        gap: 2rem;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 2rem;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
        border-radius: 15px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }

    .chapter-images {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        flex: 1;
    }

    .chapter-image {
        width: 250px;
        height: 250px;
        object-fit: cover;
        border-radius: 15px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .chapter-image:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px) scale(1.02);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    }

    .chapter-details p {
        flex: 1;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: var(--elegant-burgundy);
    }

    .journey-timeline {
        margin: 4rem 0;
        position: relative;
        padding: 2rem;
    }

    .timeline-item {
        position: relative;
        padding: 2rem;
        margin-left: 3rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        opacity: 0;
        animation: slideIn 0.8s ease-out forwards;
    }

    .timeline-marker {
        position: absolute;
        left: -20px;
        width: 40px;
        height: 40px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--love-pink), var(--romantic-pink));
        border-radius: 50%;
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 5px rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.2);
        animation: pulse 2s infinite;
    }

    .timeline-content {
        background: white;
        padding: 2rem;
        border-radius: 15px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .timeline-content:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
    }

    .timeline-content h3 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        color: var(--rich-crimson);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .timeline-content p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: var(--elegant-burgundy);
    }

    .love-moments {
        margin-top: 4rem;
    }

    .moments-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
        padding: 2rem;
    }

    .moment-card {
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        border-radius: 15px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .moment-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-10px);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    .moment-card img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 300px;
        object-fit: cover;
        transition: transform 0.5s ease;
    }

    .moment-card:hover img {
        transform: scale(1.1);
    }

    .moment-overlay {
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        padding: 2rem;
        background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.8), transparent);
        color: white;
        transform: translateY(100%);
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .moment-card:hover .moment-overlay {
        transform: translateY(0);
    }

    .love-philosophy {
        padding: 6rem 2rem;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--love-pink), var(--romantic-pink));
        border-radius: 20px;
        margin: 4rem 0;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .philosophy-content {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .philosophy-content blockquote {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
        font-style: italic;
        color: var(--elegant-burgundy);
        line-height: 1.6;
        position: relative;
        padding: 2rem;
    }

    .philosophy-content blockquote::before,
    .philosophy-content blockquote::after {
        content: '"';
        font-size: 4rem;
        color: var(--rich-crimson);
        opacity: 0.3;
        position: absolute;
    }

    .philosophy-content blockquote::before {
        top: -20px;
        left: -20px;
    }

    .philosophy-content blockquote::after {
        bottom: -40px;
        right: -20px;
    }

    @keyframes floatIn {
        from {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
        }
        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
        from {
            opacity: 0;
        }
        to {
            opacity: 1;
        }
    }

    @keyframes slideIn {
        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateX(0);
        }
    }

    @keyframes slideUp {
        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
    }

    @keyframes pulse {
        0% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.4); }
        70% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 10px rgba(220, 20, 60, 0); }
        100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(220, 20, 60, 0); }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .love-story-container {
            padding: 1rem;
        }

        .hero-section {
            height: 50vh;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .hero-content {
            width: 90%;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            background: none;
            box-shadow: none;
            backdrop-filter: none;
        }

        .lovers-name {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            color: white;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .love-subtitle {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: white;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .our-journey {
            padding: 0;
        }

        .journey-content {
            padding: 1rem;
        }

        .journey-chapter {
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        }

        .journey-chapter h2 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .chapter-details {
            display: block;
        }

        .chapter-images {
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .chapter-image {
            width: 140px;
            height: 140px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .chapter-content {
            width: 100%;
        }

        .chapter-content p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .journey-timeline {
            padding: 1rem 0;
        }

        .timeline-item {
            margin-left: 1.5rem;
            padding-left: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            position: relative;
        }

        .timeline-marker {
            width: 12px;
            height: 12px;
            left: -6px;
        }

        .timeline-content h3 {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            color: var(--elegant-burgundy);
        }

        .timeline-content p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }

        .love-philosophy {
            padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }

        .philosophy-content blockquote {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }

        .philosophy-content blockquote::before,
        .philosophy-content blockquote::after {
            font-size: 3rem;
        }

        .philosophy-content blockquote::before {
            top: -15px;
            left: -15px;
        }

        .philosophy-content blockquote::after {
            bottom: -30px;
            right: -15px;
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
        .hero-content {
            padding: 1rem;
        }

        .lovers-name {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
        }

        .love-subtitle {
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .journey-chapter h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .chapter-images {
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .chapter-image {
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
        }

        .chapter-content p {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .timeline-content h3 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .timeline-content p {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .love-philosophy {
            padding: 2rem 1rem;
        }

        .philosophy-content blockquote {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            padding: 1rem;
        }

        .philosophy-content blockquote::before,
        .philosophy-content blockquote::after {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }

        .philosophy-content blockquote::before {
            top: -10px;
            left: -10px;
        }

        .philosophy-content blockquote::after {
            bottom: -25px;
            right: -10px;
        }
    }
</style>